title: DOTA 2 The International prize pool 2011 to 2019
yAxis: Prize pool in million U.S. dollars
summary: This is a line chart with an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing Prize pool in million U.S. dollars, containing a total of 9 data points.
Overall Prize pool in million U.S. dollars has increased over the Year.
Prize pool in million U.S. dollars is roughly constant from 2011 to 2012, gradually increasing from 2012 to 2014, and lastly roughly constant from 2014 to 2019.
The highest Prize pool in million U.S. dollars, of value 34.33 was reached at Year 2019
The lowest Prize pool in million U.S. dollars, of value 1.6 was reported at Year 2011, and 2012
